nguage-text\">Debug.Log</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://unity.github.com/\">GitHub for Unity</a> - The new GitHub for Unity extension brings the GitHub workflow and more to Unity, providing support for large files with Git LFS and file locking.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/utilities/grouping-tool-147552\">Grouping Tool</a> - Easily group objects together</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mminer/scene-view-bookmarks\">Scene View Bookmarks</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/mminer/scene-view-bookmarks\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">40</span></span></a> - Editor extension to bookmark and later recall scene views.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/level-design/snazzygrid2-19245\">SnazzyGrid (Paid)</a> - Makes it easy to manage positions of assets in the scene with easy to use snapping tools and many more features to improve the scene creation workflow.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/version-control/unimerge-9733\">UniMerge (Paid)</a> - Editor extension for merging scenes and prefabs, also integrates with VCS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/neuecc/UniRx\">UniRx</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/neuecc/UniRx\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;